 MBOMBELA – A man is wanted in connection with purportedly making off with an undisclosed sum of money after agreeing to sell a trailer to an interested buyer. ALSO READ: Help the Nelspruit SAPS track down these two men According to the Nelspruit police spokesman, Capt Zandile Gqawa, the man counting the money in the video allegedly made off with the cash intended to be used as payment for a trailer.   ALSO READ: Family in court for fraud and theft The police are investigating the matter and are requesting that anyone with information about his whereabouts, contact investigating officer, Sgt Ntobeko Molewa on 072-219-7085. 